#. type: Labeled list
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/preface/_index.adoc:272
#, no-wrap
msgid "`Monospace`"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/preface/_index.adoc:274
